  <h1 style="margin-bottom:0">Arnab Nandi</h1>
  <p style="margin-top:8px">Professor, Computer Science &amp; Engineering, <br />The Ohio State University</p>
  <img src="/arnab.jpg" style="width: 180px; float: left; margin-top:10px; margin-left: -40px; margin-right: 25px; margin-bottom: 30px; transform: rotate(-5deg); shape-outside: polygon(90% 0, 5% 95%, 100% 90%);"/>
  <p>
    Email: <code>firstname at this domain</code><br/>
